asset_contract.name: Happies
asset_contract.description:
The Happies™   |   Free Mint   |   All Art Created with Microsoft Paint   |   CC0   

The year is 2022. The world has been thrown violently into a bear market; tensions are at an all-time high and depression in the crypto and NFT space is bubbling under the surface.

Then, in the darkest of blockchain despair comes a spark of joy. One little flame that burns brightly and catches wind. That little spark of joy brings hope to a fallen world and restores color and vibrancy, reminding the world that there is still something to be joyful about. 

Enter: The Happies; an entire collection build around goofy, happy-go-lucky characters saturated in joyful bliss and encouragement. If you’re looking for a P2E game, look elsewhere. If you’re after a Metaverse experience, move along. But if you want that spark of joy in your collection, then look no further.

By Yeah! Studios™   |    https://yeahstudios.io

Mint at https://mint.thehappies.io

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/yeah_studios

asset.description:
This is the official Land NFT of ArcheWorld.

This verifies that the Land NFT owner can permanently own the land designated on seamless open-world of ArcheWorld.

Owners can participate in production activities directly by installing buildings in the game, or they can lease their land to others and collect rent with Blue Salt(BSLT) every month.

Owners may generate earnings by converting Blue Salt(BSLT) to BORA.
